Handmade multi-purpose Bowl are best for serving snacks etc. This can also be used to serve dry fruits at the dinner table.These wooden Bowl are crafted for perfect shape and give very elegant look on you Dinner table. It also comes with a wooden lid. Just wipe out the bowl with soft cloth piece.

A beautiful Carved Work pen stand. A Square extended to bring you with this fine form, of a pen stand. Where you can keep all the pens, pencils and other stationary well organized.This Sheesham wood pen stand is by far stylish and different from the commonly available plastic pen stands.
